


<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<title>404 Error</title>

<style type="text/css">
html, body{
	background-color:#fff;
	
	}
.errordiv{
	width:100%;
	height:500px;
	margin-left:auto;
	margin-right:auto;
	/*background-color:#3CC;*/
	display:block;
	}
.errorimg{
	float: left;
	padding:10px;
	width: 30%;
	display: block;
	background-color: #996;
}
.errortxt{
	display: block;
	font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;
	font-size: 24px;
	font-weight: bold;
	color: #066;
	text-align: left;
	padding: 15px;
	border-bottom-width: 1px;
	border-bottom-style: dashed;
	border-bottom-color: #666;	
	/*background-color:#09C;*/
	
	}
.errortxt2{
	padding-top:20px;
	padding-left:20px;
	width:60%;
	background-color:#F90;
	float:right;
	}
.bullets{
	font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
	font-size:18px;
	font-weight:normal;
	color:#003;
	text-align:left;
	/*background-color:#F2F2F2;*/
	padding:25px;
	border-bottom-width: 1px;
	border-bottom-style: dashed;
	border-bottom-color: #666;
	}			
</style>
</head>

<body>
	<div class="errordiv">
     <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
          <tr>
            <td><img src="/auctionhome/images/404_error.png" /></td>
            <td>
            <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
              <tr>
                <td>
                <div class="errortxt">Trying to access pages through improper channel</div>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                <div class="bullets">
               <p>You are trying to access pages from Server in an unauthorised way.Any Unauthorised access will be tracked and penalised as per provisions.</p> 
               <p align="center">Or</p>
               <p>SORRY FOR THE INCONVENIENCE CAUSED.
GENERALLY MAINTENANCE IS DONE ON FIRST SATURDAY OF EVERY MONTH</p>
            </div>
                
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
		   </td>
          </tr>
        </table>

	</div>
</body>
</html>
